widgets_values: Controls how much animation there is in the output. Try values from 1 - 1.5, with a higher number for more motion.
Load your images of the text here. Number them according to the order in which you want them to appear. See example folder (controlnet) in zip.
Load your images of the background here. Number them according to the order in which you want them to appear. See example folder (images) in zip.
Important parameter here is frames. This controls the number of frames you want each image to appear. Higher number will require more VRAM.
Important parameter here is frames. This controls the number of frames you want each text to appear. Higher number will require more VRAM.
Prompt travel according to your images, make sure to leave an empty line between each prompt.

Set the video resolution of the final output.

Higher resolution will require more VRAM.
